                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.3331/337</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Press Release Issued by the Department of State, January 8,
                        1940</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-head" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1940-01-08">January 8, 1940</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>The Department of State announced today that trade-agreement negotiations with
                    Uruguay had been terminated. These negotiations have been conducted in an
                    atmosphere of the utmost friendliness and cordiality. However, because of the
                    similarity in important respects of the export trade of Uruguay and Argentina
                    with the United States, it has been found necessary, in view of the recent
                    termination of negotiations with Argentina, to terminate also the negotiations
                    with Uruguay.</p>
            </div>
